text:
One, two, three, four
Five, six, seven── Turn.
Mano, great job! You're looking lively.
Today's lesson involves wearing costumes, right?

Yes, that's right.
The new costumes with everyone...
I hope to get used to them quickly...

Well, you already seem to be fitting in
perfectly with those turns earlier.

Until you're satisfied, Mano.
Keep up the good work!

Thank you very much.
I'll do my best.
